Commercial Quoting

Easily configure, reprice, and navigate complex commercial quotes with multi-level insured item relationships and coverages.

Each insured item can have its own set of coverages and coverage terms. You can add coverages and ratings to parent, child, and grandchild insured items.

Insurance Quote Commercial Lightning Web Component

The Insurance Quote Commercial LWC is designed to help you build complex quotes. It features a side panel for editing line items and buttons for common actions, such as issuing policies and creating quote versions.

To make the Issue Policy button available, select Show Issue Policy Button on the Insurance Quote Commercial LWC in the Lightning App Builder.

This component supports multi-root quotes, which consist of a quote with multiple root products. Users can view root products and associated coverages on the same UI.

When comparing versions of a quote, the side-by-side view shows details for multiple levels of insured items in single- and multi-root quotes.

Commercial Quoting Workflow

After creating and configuring a quote, you may want to:

* Create a new commercial quote
* Configure a commercial quote to provide needed coverages
* Rate quotes as many times as needed during the quoting process
* Create and compare quote versions from a Quote record
* Issue a policy directly from a commercial quote using the Issue Policy button

Optional Coverage Rules for Quoting run when making changes to insured items, insured parties, and coverages on the Commercial Quote UI.

Commissions can be used to calculate commission data based on individual agents and products in different time periods.
title: Commercial Insurance Quoting and Policy Management
